    -->
    <para>
     Doc: mention that multi-statement queries are sent to primary node only. (<ulink url="http://www.pgpool.net/mantisbt/view.php?id=492">bug 492</>) (Tatsuo Ishii)
    </para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
