       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	fail_over_on_backend_error is off.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	ALWAYS_MASTER flags is set to the master (writer) node.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
